==English==
===Etymology===
Derived from Latin ''[[filius]]'' meaning "son" + English ''[[-cide]]''

===Noun===
{{Wikipedia}}
'''filicide'''
# A person who kills his or her own [[son]], or more generally, [[child]].
# The killing of one's own child.

====Usage note====
[[infanticide|Infanticide]] the the usual English term. 

